sequenceDiagram
    actor CUSTOMER
    participant FlaskApp as Flask Application
    participant Hotel
    participant User
    participant Feedback

    CUSTOMER->>+FlaskApp: POST /api/my_feedback (username)
    FlaskApp->>+Hotel: get_user_by_username(username)
    Hotel->>+Hotel: Find User by username
    Hotel-->>+FlaskApp: User instance
    FlaskApp->>+Hotel: get_feedback_by_customer(user)
    Hotel->>+Hotel: Find Feedback list by User
    Hotel-->>+FlaskApp: Feedback list
    alt Feedback list found
        FlaskApp->>+Feedback: Get feedback details
        loop For each feedback in feedback_list
            Feedback-->>+FlaskApp: Feedback details (id, date, customer name, rating, comment)
        end
        FlaskApp-->>-CUSTOMER: Feedback list details (200 OK)
    else Feedback list not found
        FlaskApp-->>-CUSTOMER: {"error": "Feedback not found"} (404 Not Found)
    end

    CUSTOMER->>+FlaskApp: POST /api/edit_my_feedback (username, feedback_id, rating, comment)
    FlaskApp->>+FlaskApp: Extract username, feedback_id, rating, comment from JSON request
    FlaskApp->>+Hotel: get_user_by_username(username)
    Hotel->>+Hotel: Find User by username
    Hotel-->>+FlaskApp: User instance
    FlaskApp->>+Hotel: get_feedback_by_id(feedback_id)
    Hotel->>+Hotel: Find Feedback by feedback_id
    Hotel-->>+FlaskApp: Feedback instance
    alt User and Feedback found
        FlaskApp->>+Feedback: Update feedback (rating, comment)
        Feedback->>+Feedback: Update rating and comment
        Feedback-->>+FlaskApp: "Feedback updated"
        FlaskApp-->>-CUSTOMER: {"message": "Feedback updated"} (200 OK)
    else Invalid username or feedback id
        FlaskApp-->>-CUSTOMER: {"error": "Invalid username or feedback id"} (400 Bad Request)
    end

    CUSTOMER->>+FlaskApp: POST /api/delete_my_feedback (username, feedback_id)
    FlaskApp->>+FlaskApp: Extract username, feedback_id from JSON request
    FlaskApp->>+Hotel: get_user_by_username(username)
    Hotel->>+Hotel: Find User by username
    Hotel-->>+FlaskApp: User instance
    FlaskApp->>+Hotel: get_feedback_by_id(feedback_id)
    Hotel->>+Hotel: Find Feedback by feedback_id
    Hotel-->>+FlaskApp: Feedback instance
    alt User and Feedback found
        FlaskApp->>+Hotel: delete_feedback(feedback)
        Hotel->>+Hotel: Remove feedback from records
        Hotel-->>+FlaskApp: Response (True/False)
        alt Feedback deleted successfully
            FlaskApp-->>-CUSTOMER: {"message": "Feedback deleted"} (200 OK)
        else Feedback not deleted
            FlaskApp-->>-CUSTOMER: {"error": "Feedback not deleted"} (400 Bad Request)
        end
    else Invalid username or feedback id
        FlaskApp-->>-CUSTOMER: {"error": "Invalid username or feedback id"} (400 Bad Request)
    end